name: io.bytes.per.checksum
description:
The number of bytes per checksum.  Must not be larger than
  io.file.buffer.size.

name: dfs.blockreport.intervalMsec
description: Determines block reporting interval in milliseconds.

name: ha.health-monitor.sleep-after-disconnect.ms
description: How long to sleep after an unexpected RPC error.

name: dfs.namenode.top.window.num.buckets
description: Number of buckets in the rolling window implementation of nntop

name: fs.s3a.list.version
description:
Select which version of the S3 SDK's List Objects API to use.  Currently
    support 2 (default) and 1 (older API).

name: mapreduce.task.exit.timeout.check-interval-ms
description:
The interval in milliseconds between which the MR framework
  checks if task attempts stay in finishing state for too long.
